{"tid":223024,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公司男同事集體睇咸野...","createTime":"2017-04-30T04:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T12:14:57.000Z","uid":27553,"like":2,"dislike":115,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8be8effd446bb366be62db4bfab660a3fc9b372e","tid":223024,"uid":27553,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:28:25.000Z","msg":"返左呢份工幾個月 本身個人內向 一直都好少同其他同事講野<br />\n呢間公司好少女仔 計埋我都係得3個 其他十幾個都係男同事<br />\n我都冇咩同佢地交流 多數做自己野 做完就收工<br />\n點知今朝一番工 見到五六個男同事圍埋一齊 就係我張枱對面<br />\n睇到好興奮咁 我好奇經過一望 點知一望就見到佢地睇緊D內衣照<br />\n其實我都知成班男人無咩可能唔講呢D野<br />\n但可唔可以唔好開大個mon係度睇呢?<br />\n當我地幾個女仔無到"},{"pid":"ec2fe6551a97b2127fb5e2a6a853128bf18ae9ee","tid":223024,"uid":86418,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"if you can't beat them, then join them ... hehe"},{"pid":"0de62c14f0fc8c35e61156dbfa0afa849d0bcfda","tid":223024,"uid":35072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:31:58.000Z","msg":"同佢地講囉，係度講無用架喎&hellip;"},{"pid":"49a90edf42b36ea2f8d9b996b874b5b0b019c381","tid":223024,"uid":56627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:32:48.000Z","msg":"Engine?"},{"pid":"53edb7ea47898ec369c1d70970099e19987ee7e9","tid":223024,"uid":74015,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:35:03.000Z","msg":"咁你要反省下點解班同事寧願上網睇都唔睇你喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a6999abbe09038ef77e19b5b0c4d855c35e5c4","tid":223024,"uid":98645,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T05:09:19.000Z","msg":"但其實內衣照都無乜野啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7a91e96cb70532d61c344b657bcb34151e029c","tid":223024,"uid":68060,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T05:10:05.000Z","msg":"樓主<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定係豬閪</span>"},{"pid":"1315b6ae4841e94a005e9d5e3a9cc2828f574abc","tid":223024,"uid":16616,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score"